Mark is one of the funniest comedians I know.... I grew up in the same church as Mark in Houston, TX. So I knew him even when we were children and he was very funny then and continues to bless people with his shows and his humor.

I love Mark Lowry, and his true life stories, growing up in the early 1960's, as a hyperactive child, before that term was an everyday, common word.  I was blessed to meet his "Mama and Daddy" back in 1989. and talked with Mark, several times, when he was in Indianapolis !  It's suitable for all ages.
